# Shuify - Isometric Room Planner

## Overview
- A web application that allows users to design and arrange rooms in isometric 3D view with drag-and-drop functionality.
- Ongoing learning project.

## Features
- ğŸ  Drag-and-drop furniture placement in isometric view.
